9 protegido de cualquier conflicto de inter\u00e9s, decisiones demasiado consensuadas (\u00abs\u00edndrome del sumiso\u00bb), defectos de exhibici\u00f3n individual y elevada presi\u00f3n administrativa o jer\u00e1rquica.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-eedfc2c\" data-id=\"eedfc2c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-738d9e1f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"738d9e1f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.15.0 - 20-08-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"999\" height=\"562\" src=\"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Itburrun.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-11516\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Itburrun.jpg 999w, https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Itburrun-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Itburrun-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 999px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-36130bf0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"36130bf0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-co